group emcareobservationemcareb24gde01(source src, target tgt) {

      atimestamp.value as val -> tgt.issued = val "5af77f2c";
    } "7f22f29f";
  } "aae7a11d";
  src.subject as subject -> tgt.subject = subject "patient";
  src.item first as item where (linkId = 'EmCare.B24.G.DE01') and answer.exists() then {
    item.answer first as a then {
      a.value as val ->  tgt.value = val,  tgt.status = 'final' "afa0ccc0";

  } "35db2384";
}
